{
  "page": "Further East",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Further East</b> is the region of <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> located east of the <a href=\"/index.php/Bone_Mountains\" title=\"Bone Mountains\">Bone Mountains</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sand_Sea\" title=\"Great Sand Sea\">Great Sand Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Regions_of_the_Further_East\">Regions of the Further East</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Further_East&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Regions of the Further East\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Plains_of_the_Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Plains of the Jogos Nhai\">Plains of the Jogos Nhai</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Shrinking_Sea\" title=\"Shrinking Sea\">Shrinking Sea</a></li>\n<li>The isle of <a href=\"/index.php/Leng\" title=\"Leng\">Leng</a></li>\n<li>The island of <a href=\"/index.php/Marahai\" title=\"Marahai\">Marahai</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Manticore_Isles\" title=\"Manticore Isles\">Manticore Isles</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/N%27Ghai\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"N&#39;Ghai\">N'Ghai</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mossovy\" title=\"Mossovy\">Mossovy</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Waste\" title=\"Grey Waste\">Grey Waste</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Land_of_the_Shrykes\" title=\"Land of the Shrykes\">Land of the Shrykes</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Cannibal_Sands\" title=\"Cannibal Sands\">Cannibal Sands</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Dry_Deep\" title=\"Dry Deep\">Dry Deep</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Morn\" title=\"Mountains of the Morn\">Mountains of the Morn</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Hidden_Sea\" title=\"Hidden Sea\">Hidden Sea</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Lands\" title=\"Shadow Lands\">Shadow Lands</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Sea</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Saffron_Straits\" title=\"Saffron Straits\">Saffron Straits</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ulthos\" title=\"Ulthos\">Ulthos</a></li>\n<li>The isle of <a href=\"/index.php/Ulos\" title=\"Ulos\">Ulos</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_scenes\">Behind the scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Further_East&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The term \"Further East\" is analogous to the real-life term \"Far East\", used by early modern Europeans to refer to East Asia.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Further_East&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafyi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Yi Ti.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403124414\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 104/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8542/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 297/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 43/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 522/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.989      1 -total\n 74.16%    3.700      1 Template:Ref\n 49.01%    2.445      1 Template:Ref/core\n 24.25%    1.210      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18782-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403124414 and revision id 273700\n -->\n",
